  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this research is to find ways to maximize the benefits of antipsychotic
      medications for cognition.

      Hypothesis: Risperidone and olanzapine will show greater benefits than conventional
      medications on assessments of social cognition, particularly affect perception and social
      perception.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
