  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosed with schizophrenia disorder by a DSM IV.

          -  Competent to sign informed consent

          -  No history of poor response to Risperdal and Zyprexa

          -  No organic brain disease

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Mental retardation or any chronic medical illness which results in the patient not
             being appropriate for a switch to Risperdal or Zyprexa.
      </textblock>
